select.id: get送付対象取得のデータ

mapper.select:
SELECT dbt3034.* FROM rgdb."DbT3034ShokanShinsei" AS dbt3034 WHERE
(dbt3034."sofuYM" IS NULL OR dbt3034."sofuYM" = '' OR dbt3034."kokuhorenSaisofuFlag" = true) AND (((dbt3034."kaishuShinseiKubun" IS NULL OR dbt3034."kaishuShinseiKubun" = '') AND dbt3034."shinseiYMD" IS NOT NULL AND dbt3034."shinseiYMD" <> '') OR dbt3034."kaishuShinseiKubun" = '2') AND dbt3034."serviceTeikyoYM" < #{処理年月} AND NOT EXISTS ( SELECT 'X' FROM rgdb."DbT3036ShokanHanteiKekka" AS 判定結果 WHERE 判定結果."hiHokenshaNo" = dbt3034."hiHokenshaNo" AND 判定結果."serviceTeikyoYM" = dbt3034."serviceTeikyoYM" AND 判定結果."seiriNo" = dbt3034."seiriNo" AND 判定結果."ketteiYMD" <> '' AND 判定結果."ketteiYMD" IS NOT NULL)
(dbt3034."sofuYM" IS NULL OR dbt3034."sofuYM" = '' OR dbt3034."kokuhorenSaisofuFlag" = true OR dbt3034."sofuYM" = #{処理年月}) AND (((dbt3034."kaishuShinseiKubun" IS NULL OR dbt3034."kaishuShinseiKubun" = '') AND dbt3034."shinseiYMD" IS NOT NULL AND dbt3034."shinseiYMD" <> '') OR dbt3034."kaishuShinseiKubun" = '2') AND dbt3034."serviceTeikyoYM" < #{処理年月} AND NOT EXISTS ( SELECT 'X' FROM rgdb."DbT3036ShokanHanteiKekka" AS 判定結果 WHERE 判定結果."hiHokenshaNo" = dbt3034."hiHokenshaNo" AND 判定結果."serviceTeikyoYM" = dbt3034."serviceTeikyoYM" AND 判定結果."seiriNo" = dbt3034."seiriNo" AND 判定結果."ketteiYMD" <> '' AND 判定結果."ketteiYMD" IS NOT NULL)

mapper.select:
SELECT SUB.* FROM( SELECT A.*, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY A."renban" ORDER BY A."dbT4001JukyushaDaicho_rirekiNo" DESC, A."dbT4001JukyushaDaicho_edaban" DESC ) AS rowNum FROM( SELECT , 受給者.* FROM "DbWT2111ShokanShinsei" INNER JOIN( SELECT
FROM rgdb."DbT4001JukyushaDaicho" WHERE "logicalDeletedFlag" = FALSE) AS 受給者 ON "DbWT2111ShokanShinsei"."hiHokenshaNo" = 受給者."dbT4001JukyushaDaicho_hihokenshaNo" WHERE( 受給者."dbT4001JukyushaDaicho_yukoMukoKubun" = '1' AND SUBSTR(受給者."dbT4001JukyushaDaicho_ninteiYukoKikanKaishiYMD",0,6) <= "DbWT2111ShokanShinsei"."serviceTeikyoYM" AND "DbWT2111ShokanShinsei"."serviceTeikyoYM" <= SUBSTR(受給者."dbT4001JukyushaDaicho_ninteiYukoKikanShuryoYMD",0,6)) OR (受給者."dbT4001JukyushaDaicho_kyuSochishaFlag" = TRUE AND 受給者."dbT4001JukyushaDaicho_yokaigoJotaiKubunCode" = '01')) AS A) AS SUB WHERE SUB.rowNum = 1
